<MethodEndpoint
  method={"delete"}
  path={"/api/v1.0/views/teams/{viewTeamId}"}
  context={"endpoint"}
>
  
</MethodEndpoint>



Deletes a team share assignment so the team no longer has access to the view.

**Prerequisites**
1. **viewTeamId** - Use [GET /api/v1.0/views/\{viewId\}/teams](/docs/api/views/list-view-teams) to list shares and extract `Items[].ViewTeamId`.

**Workflow Example**
1. List team shares: [GET /api/v1.0/views/\{viewId\}/teams](/docs/api/views/list-view-teams).
2. Delete the share: [DELETE /api/v1.0/views/teams/\{viewTeamId\}](/docs/api/views/delete-view-team).

**Minimal Required Fields**: `viewTeamId` (path).
